WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 21=
=The Devil From Heaven=

00:01:20.940 --> 00:01:27.940
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:39.700
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:01:44.150 --> 00:01:46.090
♪They say♪

00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:54.880
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:58.380
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:04.550
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:02:05.930 --> 00:02:11.690
♪I've already lost you♪

00:02:11.690 --> 00:02:17.790
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:21.790
♪Like a sad movie playing out♪

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:27.750
♪Bound for a tragic ending♪

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.440
So you were the one who asked me out.

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.080
I thought it was Ding Daang.

00:02:57.040 --> 00:02:58.080
It was me.

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:02.880
Nothing you want to say to me?

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.490
You already know everything.

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:07.800
Yes.

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:11.480
So you came to settle things with me?

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:12.720
No.

00:03:16.480 --> 00:03:17.880
I just want to know

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:21.160
why you're helping Ding Daang.

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:24.280
When I was nineteen,

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:26.320
I married Ding Haishan.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.800
He gave me everything.

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.320
Everything but my freedom.

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:32.680
I envied your mother.

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:34.840
Because in her,

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:36.920
I saw a woman's independence.

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:40.480
With her own hands,

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:41.800
she raised you and your sister.

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:44.560
That's something I never had done.

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.040
Not long after you left,

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:49.400
Ding Haishan went bankrupt.

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:52.590
I walked away from the Ding family.

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:19.000
Ding Daang.

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:26.760
For your daughter's treatment.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.560
How could I take your money?

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.720
I was so foolish back then.

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:34.360
I hurt you,

00:04:34.840 --> 00:04:35.680
your father,

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:38.280
and even you.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.640
I want to ask you for a favor.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.440
Since you've also got regrets,

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:53.480
let's settle all that old mess together.

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:07.720
So,

00:05:07.720 --> 00:05:09.760
do you think we should tell Ding Daang?

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:14.360
Maybe we should just stay out of it.

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.280
Sometimes

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:16.520
silence is better.

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:19.280
About that inheritance,

00:05:19.280 --> 00:05:20.840
it never really existed, did it?

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:24.360
Right.

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.960
She build everything she has now

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:28.880
on her own.

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:31.680
On top of that, she even paid off

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.120
the debt her father left behind,

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:34.640
over twenty million in total.

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:36.760
We've all been pretending,

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.320
but what she's done is for you.

00:05:40.200 --> 00:05:42.320
It's to help you heal.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.200
So,

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:59.520
she asked you to come back

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:02.880
to trigger Chen Aming's memories

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:06.320
and drive away Yu Kun's existence.

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:08.240
That's not true.

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:10.640
She did it so your existence
could be whole again.

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:13.160
She said no matter if you're Yu Kun

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.120
or Chen Aming,

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:15.600
you still have to face your past

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.080
to create a future.

00:06:22.360 --> 00:06:23.400
Facing the past?

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:25.600
Chen Aming,

00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:27.160
I know you didn't really want to

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:28.560
break up with Ding Daang.

00:06:30.440 --> 00:06:31.680
Now Ding Daang has given me

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:32.560
a second chance.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.640
She's given you one, too.

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:37.520
This time, you have to treat her right.

00:06:39.520 --> 00:06:41.280
She deserves the best in this world.

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:42.400
The best person.

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:46.840
No matter what that "best" actually means.

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:48.400
Yes.

00:06:50.320 --> 00:06:51.640
She deserves to be treated right.

00:06:53.720 --> 00:06:55.360
There's one more thing I want to tell you.

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:59.320
Even though I know it might sound

00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:00.040
a bit hollow

00:07:00.040 --> 00:07:01.240
and maybe even ridiculous,

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:04.440
I still want to say to you

00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:07.280
and your family—I'm sorry.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:08.120
No need.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:11.840
Alright.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:16.160
What are your plans moving forward?

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.040
We...

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.200
We...

00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:29.840
We're getting married.

00:07:32.840 --> 00:07:33.760
Wish you all the best.

00:07:34.320 --> 00:07:35.160
Thanks.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:18.440
You're here.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:25.920
What is it?

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:26.800
A love letter?

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:28.800
The bar tab I still owe you.

00:08:31.320 --> 00:08:32.800
You know I don't care about that.

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.800
But I do care.

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:39.480
I'm leaving soon.

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:42.640
I never really belonged anywhere.

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:44.920
Though,

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:46.720
Keep Love did give me a home.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:49.720
But that was only temporary.

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:51.400
What if

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:53.840
I could give you a home too?

00:08:57.400 --> 00:08:58.480
You know what I mean.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.120
I've never really understood love.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.480
It's like a bug that never gets fixed.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.240
Then let's fix it together.

00:09:08.160 --> 00:09:09.000
Lin Xibei.

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:11.040
I like you.

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:13.200
What is it that you like about me?

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:14.880
Everything.

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:18.000
You're such a fool, aren't you?

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.160
I'll take good care of you.

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:23.280
I've signed up for a class.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.360
What kind of class?

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:30.640
A cooking class.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.920
I want to make all the delicious dishes

00:09:34.020 --> 00:09:35.040
you've never tried before.

00:10:01.400 --> 00:10:02.520
Hey there, my darlings!

00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:04.560
Welcome back to the Keep Love Channel.

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:06.280
Today's topic is special.

00:10:06.280 --> 00:10:08.600
When someone loves another person,

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:10.200
what should they do for them?

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.040
That's right.

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:12.600
Love isn't just about sweet words.

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:14.480
It's also about actions and effort.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.680
So, Mr. Zhou,

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:17.400
what do you think someone should do

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:18.760
when they're in love?

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:21.120
I'd say… be there for their loves.

00:10:21.560 --> 00:10:23.200
Just like I join you
for every livestream,

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:24.060
no matter the weather.

00:10:24.060 --> 00:10:25.040
Come on, cut it out.

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:25.900
With or without me,

00:10:25.900 --> 00:10:26.750
you'll stream anyway.

00:10:26.750 --> 00:10:27.640
Hey, that's not fair.

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:28.920
I'm being totally sincere here.

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:30.120
Actually,

00:10:30.120 --> 00:10:31.800
loving someone is really simple.

00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:33.380
Like remembering what they like

00:10:33.380 --> 00:10:34.400
and what they can't stand.

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:37.080
Most importantly, being there

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:38.560
when they need you most.

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:41.080
Like this?

00:10:44.280 --> 00:10:45.720
When did you get all this ready?

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:46.920
It's a secret.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:48.200
To love someone

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:50.000
is to surprise her whenever you can.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:50.840
Am I right?

00:11:00.880 --> 00:11:01.720
Ding Daang,

00:11:04.280 --> 00:11:05.440
you said we'd last forever

00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:08.520
and I said yes.

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.320
Now it's my turn to ask you.

00:11:18.840 --> 00:11:19.760
Marry me.

00:11:21.520 --> 00:11:22.600
No contracts.

00:11:23.480 --> 00:11:24.440
No schemes.

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:30.040
Just you and me.

00:11:32.640 --> 00:11:33.560
Will you?

00:11:38.020 --> 00:11:40.600
♪That song suddenly started playing♪

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:43.350
♪And I thought of you again♪

00:11:44.150 --> 00:11:49.060
♪Even though I swore to the world
we were done♪

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:52.680
♪All my friends laughed at me♪

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:55.860
♪Why can't I just let it go♪

00:11:57.360 --> 00:12:01.380
♪But how could they ever know
how good you were to me♪

00:12:01.770 --> 00:12:04.780
♪I'm falling into
the swamp of your charm♪

00:12:05.030 --> 00:12:07.680
♪It's painful yet feels so right♪

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:10.410
♪As the endless night unfolds♪

00:12:10.410 --> 00:12:13.140
♪I toss and turn, can't fall asleep♪

00:12:14.870 --> 00:12:18.060
♪You keep running through my mind♪

00:12:18.060 --> 00:12:21.120
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

00:12:21.370 --> 00:12:22.500
♪Why?♪

00:12:22.890 --> 00:12:26.650
♪You walked out of my world♪

00:12:26.960 --> 00:12:29.790
♪You are my only cure♪

00:12:29.950 --> 00:12:33.210
♪Can you give me one more hug?♪

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:39.260
♪Did you hear me say please don't go♪

00:12:41.090 --> 00:12:43.490
♪That song keeps playing on repeat♪

00:12:44.050 --> 00:12:46.400
♪Feels like
everything has frozen in time♪

00:12:47.050 --> 00:12:52.250
♪Where our happy moments were buried♪

00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:55.680
♪I wonder what you're doing now♪

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:58.670
♪Are you really happier than before?♪

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:01.960
Alright.

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:04.200
You've watched it like 800 times.

00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:07.200
So? Still think it's good?

00:13:07.220 --> 00:13:09.930
♪Let it be.
Maybe I was just holding on too tight♪

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.080
Where's your watch?

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:11.920
I threw it away.

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:15.000
Didn't you used to wear it all the time?

00:13:17.560 --> 00:13:18.520
My dear wife.

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:19.680
Let me tell you.

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:22.680
Don't act innocent
after getting what you wanted.

00:13:24.140 --> 00:13:25.280
♪Why?♪

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:26.920
Got it.

00:13:26.920 --> 00:13:27.760
Honey.

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:29.800
What?

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:32.040
Hon...

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:33.520
...ey.

00:13:33.660 --> 00:13:35.840
♪Can you give me one more hug?♪

00:13:37.910 --> 00:13:41.100
♪Did you hear me say please don't go♪

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:41.960
Keep going.

00:13:41.970 --> 00:13:44.670
♪My world once shined because of you♪

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:47.650
♪I even forgot how small I was♪

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:50.670
♪As long as
there's still fire in my heart♪

00:13:50.950 --> 00:13:53.130
♪I won't let tears blur my eyes♪

00:13:53.160 --> 00:13:54.020
I wanna touch this.

00:13:54.030 --> 00:13:56.640
♪Silently I pray for you♪

00:13:56.960 --> 00:14:00.040
♪Wishing you a better life than mine♪

00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:03.040
Ding Daang.

00:14:03.520 --> 00:14:04.840
Do you remember when we eloped?

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:09.880
How about we

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:11.640
doing it again?

00:14:12.200 --> 00:14:13.320
I'm Yu Kun.

00:14:16.440 --> 00:14:17.520
I'm Chen Aming too.

00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:19.320
Ding Daang.

00:14:20.120 --> 00:14:20.960
Tell me.

00:14:22.560 --> 00:14:23.680
Is this what you really want?

00:14:26.040 --> 00:14:26.880
Is it?

00:14:58.300 --> 00:15:05.300
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:17.060
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:15:21.500 --> 00:15:23.460
♪They say♪

00:15:23.860 --> 00:15:32.260
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:15:32.780 --> 00:15:35.740
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:15:35.980 --> 00:15:41.900
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:15:43.300 --> 00:15:49.060
♪I've already lost you♪

00:15:49.060 --> 00:15:54.540
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:15:54.820 --> 00:16:00.780
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:16:00.780 --> 00:16:05.580
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:16:06.660 --> 00:16:10.700
♪The past will always pass♪

00:16:11.020 --> 00:16:18.620
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:16:19.100 --> 00:16:22.340
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:16:22.900 --> 00:16:28.540
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:16:31.020 --> 00:16:34.540
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:16:34.540 --> 00:16:40.780
♪But sadly, it's not you♪